00:01:42.790 --> 00:01:47.384
 This will be true for coming ages, 

00:01:48.172 --> 00:01:51.707
 not only for the millions living now, 

00:01:51.707 --> 00:01:55.629
 but also for the millions that are yet to be born. 

00:01:57.721 --> 00:02:00.453
 Shouldn't we stop the bleeding? 

